description: The index tracks the performance of globally exchange-listed equities of companies across the globe that are engaged in “Travel Technology Business” which is defined as providing technology. The fund invests at least 80% of its net assets in financial instruments, securities of the index, and exchange-traded funds that track the index and other financial instruments that provide daily leveraged exposure to the index or to ETFs that track the index. It is non-diversified.
name: ETFMG 2x Daily Travel Tech ETF
